tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All parameters are within normal limits except for a markedly low HbA1c (3.3%), which may indicate recent hypoglycemia, anemia, or altered red cell turnover. Glucose is at the lower end of normal. Renal and electrolyte values are unremarkable. Correlate clinically for possible hypoglycemia or underlying hematologic conditions.
